I hate having to spend my day wearing a mask and literally coming home with a sore throat due to that mask. 6 feet my hind-end! Plus, the stupid hospitals like Kaiser Permanente are advocating for these COVID-19 lockdowns and measures when COVID-19 has LITERALLY a less than 3% chance of being dangerous (yes, I actually did the math, thanks for asking). I'd rather be sick with a cold knowing that it's worse than a coronavirus than be locked up in a shed over a virus that I may or may not catch.
